Description
-----------
Mean is computed using static/dynamic library, variables are passed from the main/driver program.

Steps for compilation
---------------------
1. make 
To generate static & dynamic libraries and respective executables.

2. make static_lib
To generate static library and executable.

3. ./static_lib.o
To run executable.

4. make shared_lib
To generate shared library and executable.

5. ./shared_lib.o
To run executable.

6. make clean
To remove and .o, .a and .so files.


Output
------
 Result: 
 a=2.20  b=4.40  Mean=3.30
